<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> Somumario diritto malechita: Guidi- Santillana، جـ ٢، ص ٢٨٥ وما بعدها.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> Derecho Musulman: Lopez Ortiz ص ١٩٢ وما بعدها.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
